description:
The Fighting Yank

Table of Contents Description - A city of heroes--prostate beneath the awful menace of The Claw! Only one man--The Fighting Yank--dared face his awful talons--and rip the shroud of death from a chilling mystery!

Story Description - Howland was a peaceful, charming little city, proud of its heritage and its war heroes! Then The Claw appeared from the shadows to wrap the town in a deadly mantle of fear! Did he get away with his diabolical scheme? Well, The Claw though he held all the cards-- until The Fighting Yank decided to deal him out!

Portable Landing Field (Text Only Story)

Front Page Peggy

Table of Contents Description - A man who didn't want his picture in the paper--why? A thug who built his own version of the electric chair--for what? Peggy runs into a real thriller this time--and digs up the answers in the greatest scoop of her career!

Story Description - Peggy's flair for ferreting out exclusive news stories here puts her at odds with three vicious killers ...and threatens to put her own name in the obituary columns!

You Just Can't Win! (One Page Comic)

The Praying Mantis (Text Only Story)

Pyroman

Table of Contents Description - Like taking pictures? Dick Martin and Joyce did, too--little dreaming that a simple lens could point the way towards a diabolical and earth-shaking plot! Yes, it's a situation which screams for Pyroman--and all of his blazing super-powers!

Story Description - With thousands of volts of electricity stored in his body after a research accident, Dick Martin uses his sizzling energy as Pyroman-- the human dynamo who meets crime with fiery bolts more powerful than lightning!

Wooden Surprise (Text Only Story)

Trouble-Shooter

Table of Contents Description - Ever hear of the Kohmar Ruby? Galahad Grant hadn't, either--until a beautiful actress launched him on his greatest case! Watch our Trouble-Shooter court deadly danger in a bangup manhunt!

Story Description - A strange combination of circumstances brings hard-boiled, hard-fisted detective Galahad Grant into the most exciting mystery of a career dedicated to exciting mysteries! The circumstances include a huge Zircon Emerald, a smuggling ring, an almost clueless murder, and a lovely actress who... but read it for yourself!
